---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Almag - AI Safety Governance">
	<div class="bg-mesh"></div>
	<div class="bg-grid"></div>

	<section class="project-hero container animate-fade-in">
		<div class="hero-layout">
			<div class="hero-left">
				<div class="mono-label animate-fade-in">// 001 // SEC_GOVERNANCE</div>
				<h1 class="project-title animate-fade-in">
					AL<span class="text-outline">MAG</span>
				</h1>
				<p class="hero-desc animate-fade-in">
					WE ENGINEER ENFORCEABLE RELEASE GATES THROUGH SPATIAL LOGIC AND ADVANCED RISK_TRIAGE_OPS.
				</p>
				<div class="hero-actions animate-fade-in" style="animation-delay: 0.2s">
					<a href="https://github.com/almag" target="_blank" class="btn-circle">
						<svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="7" y1="17" x2="17" y2="7"></line><polyline points="7 7 17 7 17 17"></polyline></svg>
					</a>
					<span class="mono-label">EXPLORE_SOURCE_CORE</span>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="hero-right animate-fade-in" style="animation-delay: 0.4s">
				<div class="tech-stats glass-card">
					<div class="stat-item">
						<span class="mono-label">AVAILABILITY</span>
						<p>PRODUCTION_READY</p>
					</div>
					<div class="stat-item">
						<span class="mono-label">VERSION_FIX</span>
						<p>V2.1.0-STABLE</p>
					</div>
					<div class="stat-item">
						<span class="mono-label">LICENSE_TYPE</span>
						<p>MIT_OPEN_SOURCE</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="project-details container">
		<div class="details-grid">
			<article class="main-content animate-fade-in" style="animation-delay: 0.6s">
				<span class="mono-label">// THE_SOLUTION_CORE</span>
				<h2>THE SAFETY RAIL FOR <br/> AI_ACCELERATED_DEV</h2>
				<p>ALMAG ANSWERS THE ONE HARD QUESTION FOR EVERY RELEASE: "CAN WE SHIP SAFELY RIGHT NOW?" AS DEVELOPMENT ACCELERATES, ALMAG AGGREGATES SIGNALS INTO AN ACTIONABLE DECISION ENGINE WITH FULL OWNERSHIP AND TRACEABILITY.</p>
				
				<div class="capability-grid">
					<div class="capability-item glass-card">
						<span class="mono-label">01 // CORE_ENGINE</span>
						<h3>DECISION_NODE</h3>
						<p>Automated Go/No-Go signals based on active risks and organizational policies.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="capability-item glass-card">
						<span class="mono-label">02 // OWNERSHIP</span>
						<h3>TRIAGE_FLOW_OPS</h3>
						<p>Assign clear owners to every finding to eliminate risk ambiguity.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="capability-item glass-card">
						<span class="mono-label">03 // METRICS</span>
						<h3>SLA_TRACKER_GS</h3>
						<p>Automated fix deadlines based on severity to maintain security posture.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="capability-item glass-card">
						<span class="mono-label">04 // INPUT_SYNC</span>
						<h3>UNIFIED_INGEST</h3>
						<p>Ingestion for Trivy, Gitleaks, Grype, Semgrep, and custom SARIF.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</article>
			
			<aside class="sidebar animate-fade-in" style="animation-delay: 0.8s">
				<div class="glass-card side-info">
					<span class="mono-label">// TECH_STACK_OPS</span>
					<ul class="tag-list">
						<li>GO (GOLANG)</li>
						<li>REACT / VITE</li>
						<li>SQLITE_DB</li>
						<li>DOCKER_IMG</li>
						<li>GHA_CI_CD</li>
					</ul>
					<div class="divider"></div>
					<a href="/media_vault" class="btn btn-primary">TECHNICAL_DOCS_GS</a>
				</div>
			</aside>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="project-preview container animate-fade-in" style="animation-delay: 1s">
		<div class="glass-card preview-card">
			<span class="mono-label">// TECHNICAL_PREVIEW // SYSTEM_DEMO_v2.1</span>
			<div class="video-aspect">
				<iframe 
					width="100%" 
					height="100%" 
					src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/sFr7Uynu8GY" 
					title="ALMAG_SEC_GATE_DEMO" 
					frameborder="0" 
					allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" 
					allowfullscreen>
				</iframe>
			</div>
			<div class="preview-info">
				<p>REAL-TIME DEMONSTRATION OF ALMAG ENFORCING PRODUCTION SAFETY RAILS WITHIN A DISTRIBUTED CI_CD ENVIRONMENT.</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<style>
		.project-preview {
			padding: 0 0 15rem;
		}

		.preview-card {
			padding: 6rem;
		}

		.video-aspect {
			aspect-ratio: 16 / 9;
			background: #000;
			margin: 4rem 0;
			border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
		}

		.preview-info p {
			font-family: var(--font-mono);
			font-size: 0.95rem;
			color: var(--text-muted);
			text-align: center;
			letter-spacing: 0.05em;
		}

		.project-hero {
			padding: 15rem 0 10rem;
			min-height: 80vh;
			display: flex;
			align-items: center;
		}

		.hero-layout {
			display: grid;
			grid-template-columns: 1.2fr 0.8fr;
			gap: 8rem;
			width: 100%;
		}

		.project-title {
			line-height: 0.85;
			margin: 2.5rem 0;
			letter-spacing: -0.06em;
		}

		.hero-desc {
			font-family: var(--font-mono);
			font-size: 0.95rem;
			color: var(--text-muted);
			max-width: 450px;
			letter-spacing: 0.05em;
			line-height: 1.8;
			margin-bottom: 4.5rem;
		}

		.hero-actions {
			display: flex;
			align-items: center;
			gap: 3rem;
		}

		.tech-stats {
			display: flex;
			flex-direction: column;
			gap: 4.5rem;
			border-radius: 0;
			border-left: 1px solid var(--accent-primary);
			padding: 6rem 4rem;
		}

		.stat-item p {
			font-size: 1.6rem;
			font-weight: 950;
			margin-top: 1rem;
		}

		.project-details {
			padding: 8rem 0 15rem;
		}

		.details-grid {
			display: grid;
			grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr;
			gap: 10rem;
		}

		h2 {
			font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 4.2rem);
			margin: 2.5rem 0;
			letter-spacing: -0.02em;
			line-height: 1;
		}

		.capability-grid {
			display: grid;
			grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
			gap: 2rem;
			margin-top: 6rem;
		}

		.capability-item {
			padding: 4rem;
		}

		.capability-item h3 {
			font-size: 1.8rem;
			margin: 1.5rem 0 1.2rem;
			letter-spacing: -0.02em;
		}

		.capability-item p {
			font-size: 1rem;
			color: var(--text-muted);
			line-height: 1.6;
		}

		.tag-list {
			display: flex;
			flex-direction: column;
			gap: 1.5rem;
			margin: 3rem 0;
		}

		.tag-list li {
			font-family: var(--font-mono);
			font-size: 0.85rem;
			color: var(--text-color);
			display: flex;
			align-items: center;
			gap: 1rem;
		}

		.tag-list li::before {
			content: '>';
			color: var(--accent-primary);
		}

		.divider {
			height: 1px;
			background: var(--border-color);
			margin: 3rem 0;
		}

		@media (max-width: 992px) {
			.hero-layout {
				grid-template-columns: 1fr;
				gap: 5rem;
			}
			.details-grid {
				grid-template-columns: 1fr;
				gap: 5rem;
			}
			.tech-stats {
				border-left: none;
				border-top: 1px solid var(--accent-primary);
			}
		}

		@media (max-width: 768px) {
			.project-title {
				font-size: 4.5rem;
			}
			.capability-grid {
				grid-template-columns: 1fr;
			}
		}
	</style>
</Layout>
